===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Originally written {{zh-l|*㡿}}, a {{Han compound|广|屰|c1=s|c2=p|t1=building|t2=|ls=psc|nocap=y}}.

The {{zh-l|*屰}} later came to be written {{zh-l|*干}}, and the {{zh-l|*广}} was sometimes written as {{zh-l|*厂}}, eventually leading to the modern form of the character.

Alternatively, may be derived from {{zh-l|*宅}}.

